                <h1>The energy and talent behind Hoof &#039;n&#039; Horn&#039;s &#039;The Producers&#039;</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/41cc761b-5771-46dc-907d-bc68be52f4fb.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Student-run&#x20;theater&#x20;group&#x20;Hoof&#x20;&#x27;n&#x27;&#x20;Horn&#x27;s&#x20;musical&#x20;&quot;The&#x20;Producers&quot;&#x20;runs&#x20;Oct.&#x20;12-15&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;Sheafer&#x20;Lab&#x20;Theater.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Student-run theater group Hoof 'n' Horn's musical "The Producers" runs Oct. 12-15 in the Sheafer Lab Theater.</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
                                                                                    Photo by <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/multizam-oliver">Multizam Oliver</a> |
