                        <p><em>“The Producers” will run Thursday, Oct. 12 through Saturday, Oct. 14 at 8:00 p.m. in Sheafer Lab Theater, with two 2:00 pm matinees Saturday, Oct. 14 and Sunday, Oct. 15. There will be an 11:00 a.m. revue of the show Saturday, Oct. 21 in Nelson Music Room for Family Weekend.&nbsp;</em></p>
